    "course_title": "RAD LAB - DIAGNOSTIC RADIOLOGICAL PHYSICS",
    "description": "Provides hands on experience using and testing radiographic, fluoroscopic and mammographic x-ray systems.  Imaging requirements, image quality, and radiation dose aspects of each modality are covered, along with practical methods for evaluating the performance of clinical units.",
